messages.speech: Century College values your feedback regarding its positive learning environment and we recognize that from time to time, you may have a concern that needs to be addressed. We take all student concerns seriously and are committed to helping you address the concern. If you have a concern, it must be substantial, compelling, and verifiable. To address this concern and access more details about this topic, please go to  "My Century" (https://my.century.edu/Pages/default.aspx) and click on "My Tools" and choose "Student Concerns". This will help you navigate through Century's process for handling student concerns/complaints.
